on &amp; came to the same conclusion.<br><br>Quite a disapointment.<br><br>Someone posted in another thread that they thought Gorenaire spawned three days after a server patch, and then three days after she was last slain.<br><br>I'm requesting information any folks might have for the non-triggered Faydedar here too.<br><br>Tyrex <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/udareroxor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DareRoxor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(6/18/01 5:56:21 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathholyswordsandquests.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3054.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Aye</span><hr size=1> Talanshar!?<br>Karana, Talanshar, Lords of Fallen Virtue Talanshar!? If this isnt you then dont mind me, but if it is, whats goin on man? I havent talked to you since I split to Terris.<br>If you dont remember me or you werent ever on karana then dont mind me, haha. =) <p></head><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF"><p align="center"><imgsrc="http://www.chucklez.net/fencon/daresig55.jpg" width="124"height="203"></p><div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"bordercolor="#FFFFFF" bordercolordark="#FFFFFF"bordercolorlight="#FFFFFF">    <tr>        <td><a        href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=60840"><strong>Dare        Roxor</strong></a></td>        <td><a        href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=65637"><strong>Stablinger        </strong><font size="3"><strong>Halfuber</strong></font></a></td>    </tr>    <tr>        <td><em>55 Paladin</em></td>        <td><em>25 Rogue</em></td>    </tr>    <tr>        <td><strong>Terris Thule</strong></td>        <td>&nb